                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Hay</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Eddy</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1904-12-15">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 15, 1904</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Hay requests to be informed of the time limit within which appeals to the
                    admiralty court must be taken by American claimants in seizure cases.)</p>
            </div>
